gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Magic 108, Timberwolves 106
gameRecap.excerpt: The Magic defeated the Timberwolves, 108-106. Paolo Banchero recorded 23 points and six assists for the Magic, while Franz Wagner added 19 points, four rebounds and five assists in the victory. Anthony Edwards (22 points, five assists) and Rudy Gobert (22 points, 16 rebounds) combined for 44 points for the Timberwolves in the losing effort. The Magic improve to 26-23 on the season, while the Timberwolves fall to 34-15.
